Elise Neal https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elise_Neal 0 Elise Demetria Neal (born March 14, 1966) is an American actress. Her big break came in 1997, appearing in the films Rosewood, Money Talks and Scream 2. From 1998 to 2002, Neal starred as Yvonne Hughley in the ABC/UPN sitcom The Hughleys. She also has appeared in films including Restaurant (1998), Mission to Mars (2000), Paid in Full (2002), Hustle Flow (2005), and Logan (2017). On television, Neal also starred as Tia Jewel in the first two seasons of the UPN/The CW sitcom All of Us from 2003 to 2005. She also played many other roles on film and television.
